# Authors & Contributors

## でじたるそう — Te Papa Matihiko v1.0

---

## Primary Creator

### Eric Hadfield
**Role**: Original Architect, Designer, Creator
**Contribution**: Complete system design, philosophy, implementation, and documentation

Eric Hadfield is the sole creator and architect of Te Papa Matihiko. He designed the entire three-strata model, implemented the 4GR-FSE engine, developed the zero-trust security framework, and wrote all accompanying documentation.

---

## Intellectual & Philosophical Foundations

### Conceptual Frameworks
- **Three-Strata Model** — すう (Te Tau), あは (Te Āhua), れれ (Te Rere)
- **Kotahitanja Principle** — Unity and coherence measurement
- **4GR-FSE Architecture** — GROUND/READ/GATE/GROW finite state machine
- **Zero-Trust Framework** — Digital Thymus security model
- **Tri-Language Structure** — 日本語 × Te Reo Māori × English

All conceptual frameworks and philosophical foundations originated with Eric Hadfield.

### Symbolic & Mathematical Framework
- **Wobble Constants** — 0.05, 0.075, 0.15 (locked across all systems)
- **Merkle Tree Architecture** — Cryptographic root anchor
- **90-Day Temporal Lock** — Synchronization and expiry mechanism
- **Kotahitanja Coherence** — H = (1/3)*w_suu + (1/3)*w_aha + (1/3)*w_rere = 91.7%

All mathematical models and symbolic frameworks are original work by Eric Hadfield.

---

## Implementation & Development

### Core Engine
- **4GR-FSE Finite State Machine** (TypeScript)
- **4GR-FSE HTTP API Server** (TypeScript)
- **Lock Validation Logic** (TypeScript)
- **Lock Initialization & Generation** (TypeScript/Node.js)

All core engine implementation by Eric Hadfield.

### Security Framework
- **Digital Thymus Core** — Four-layer zero-trust model (Python)
- **Digital Thymus API** — Flask REST API (Python)
- **Security Policy Framework** — Risk scoring and enforcement
- **Merkle Tree Integrity** — Cryptographic verification

All security implementation by Eric Hadfield.

### Audit & Monitoring
- **MCP v2 Audit Suite** — 20 microservices (Python)
- **MCP Audit Server** — Flask-based logging (Python)
- **Prometheus Integration** — Metrics collection
- **Grafana Dashboards** — Observability
- **Lock Status Monitoring** — Real-time status script (Bash)

All audit and monitoring systems by Eric Hadfield.

### Deployment & Configuration
- **Docker Compose Configuration** — Full 14-engine deployment
- **Dockerfile Specifications** — Multiple container images
- **Kubernetes Manifests** — K8s Secret and ConfigMap
- **Environment Configuration** — .env.lock and lock-metadata

All deployment configurations by Eric Hadfield.

